data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!Spectacular Views from this Bear Valley Springs A-Frame! Lots of Solar for this mostly electric home! 13.54 kW DC Solar System with 43 Solar Panels, 2 inverters and 1 back up battery provides the Electricity at well below the going SCE rate! (Owner is currently paying 0.19 cents per kWh - instead of the going 0.36 - 0.60 cents/kWh ) Also, Keeping your EV Car charged is a breeze with the Electric Car Home Charging Option (14-50 outlet), not to mention being Energy Efficient with your Solar Panels!Nestled in the Oaks not far from the Clubhouse, Pool and Tennis Courts this Cabin-like getaway with wood beamed ceilings gives you that warm cozy feeling. Cozy up to the woodstove in the living room when the weather is cold! The open loft has been used as a bedroom. The large open kitchen with bar looks down into living room. Tile and Laminate wood flooring throughout and large master bedroom with walk in closet. The master bathroom has a garden tub, separate shower and double vanity sinks. This could be great second or starter home situated on a little over an acre. 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a large office with over 2200 sqft of living space.Buyer will need to assume the Solar PPA (current monthly cost is $260)
